	<ofx:title lang="en">File Export</ofx:title>
	
	<ofx:paragraph lang="en">
		The system is able to export data in different file formats. The export is started by
		clicking the appropriate icon. The the system will generate the desired file and directly
		start a download in the browser. The behavior on how this is handled on the client side
		depends on the browser and personal settings of the user for his browser.
		A common behavior is to store the file in 
		<text:emphasis italic="true">Downloads</text:emphasis> folder or to directly
		open it.
	</ofx:paragraph>

	
